00:22:12.740 --> 00:22:16.280
with a clinical and research focus on bladder

390
00:22:16.360 --> 00:22:19.860
cancer. His pioneering research has centered on

391
00:22:19.900 --> 00:22:23.790
approaches to escalate and deescalate treatments based on

392
00:22:23.820 --> 00:22:25.980
response adaptive treatment paradigms.

