00:49:28.544 --> 00:49:32.224
This is a patient with metastatic bladder cancer treated with first-line

836
00:49:32.244 --> 00:49:36.104
therapy. And as you can see, the cancer initially responds only

837
00:49:36.164 --> 00:49:39.784
to relapse despite continued treatment in just

838
00:49:39.884 --> 00:49:41.604
sometimes a matter of a few weeks.

839
00:49:42.624 --> 00:49:46.464
And in many of these cases, it's our practice and in many

840
00:49:46.524 --> 00:49:48.664
other tertiary cancer centers,

841
00:49:49.864 --> 00:49:53.564
the practice is to obtain next generation whole

