846
00:50:06.644 --> 00:50:10.524
So, and we decided to try to

847
00:50:10.964 --> 00:50:14.024
model drug resistance to recapitulate the clinical

848
00:50:14.034 --> 00:50:17.724
scenario. But how can we do that? So we think there are four key

849
00:50:17.784 --> 00:50:20.964
