850
00:50:21.084 --> 00:50:24.684
centimeter tumor in diameter has close to a billion

851
00:50:24.724 --> 00:50:28.634
cancer cells in their body. So our system has to have a similar

852
00:50:28.704 --> 00:50:32.164
scale to capture the clonal evolution dynamics of these rare

853
00:50:32.184 --> 00:50:33.204
resistant clones.

854
00:50:34.124 --> 00:50:38.044
Second, we need sustained drug pressure over clinically relevant

855
00:50:38.104 --> 00:50:42.064
timescales. Usually, these are measured in weeks to month to mirror the

856
00:50:42.104 --> 00:50:44.664
