872
00:51:40.424 --> 00:51:43.804
It's constant drug selection of more than a billion cancer cells.

873
00:51:44.374 --> 00:51:48.364
The cells are labeled with heritable antiviral barcodes that track the

874
00:51:48.404 --> 00:51:52.104
emergence of drug resistance over time.

875
00:51:52.184 --> 00:51:55.984
These are cell tag barcodes that are developed by Sam Morris's

876
00:51:56.044 --> 00:51:59.664
group, and these are transcribable and heritable antiviral

877
00:51:59.724 --> 00:52:03.484
barcodes. Because they are transcribable, we can perform single-cell

878
00:52:03.644 --> 00:52:07.604
RNA sequencing to discover gene expression changes in the

879
00:52:07.644 --> 00:52:09.884
clonally expansive populations.

880
00:52:09.924 --> 00:52:13.384
These cells are also serially imaged over time to detect any

881
00:52:13.404 --> 00:52:14.624
morphological changes.

882
00:52:15.804 --> 00:52:19.624
One of the main questions that we developed Evo Signals to investigate

883
00:52:19.744 --> 00:52:23.164
is to dissect how cancer heterogeneity acts as a

884
00:52:23.184 --> 00:52:24.964
