888
00:52:36.224 --> 00:52:39.794
We recently showed that APOBEC-3 activity in bladder cancer is

889
00:52:39.844 --> 00:52:43.374
early and clonal, arising before exposure to

890
00:52:43.384 --> 00:52:47.244
