00:55:38.464 --> 00:55:42.404
resistant state? And because we can directly track

939
00:55:42.414 --> 00:55:46.364
these clonally expansive populations, so the population that gave rise to

940
00:55:46.384 --> 00:55:49.964
descendants over time using the Cell Takt barcodes,

